                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Campbell</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Orleans, La.,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-05-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 15, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My messenger, White, left San Luis Potosi 23d of April, and arrived here this
                    morning. He reports Maximilian with force of fifteen thousand holding Queretaro,
                    surrounded by a liberal force of thirty-five thousand. Imperialists still held
                    Vera Cruz and city of Mexico. Juarez expects to reach the city of Mexico in
                    three or four months. Mr. White brings me despatch from minister of foreign
                    affairs, defending the execution of prisoners at Zacatecas, and intimating that
                    similar severity may be practiced on Maximilian and his leading chieftains, if
                    captured. I send you full despatch by mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LEWIS D. CAMPBELL.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
